{"tid":1740484,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"［黃色經濟圈］將無國界嘅長期捐款轉去國際特赦","createTime":"2019-11-20T02:55:41.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-21T06:44:26.000Z","uid":12185,"like":41,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"1a457a18a99406f8aee2e59e3a51f08dba570548","tid":1740484,"uid":12185,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-20T02:55:41.000Z","msg":"相信好多有錢香港人係慣左set個每月捐款唔再理<br />\n如果本身係捐俾宣明會、無國界等等<br />\n可以考慮轉俾國際特赦<br />\n佢地今次嘅工作功不可沒<br />\n當然優先應該係捐星火等等直接幫抗爭者組織<br />\n但如果啲有錢黃絲有好多錢剩又唔捐國際野唔舒服，<br />\n不如轉去國際特赦"},{"pid":"0b1e87e1b9259093a4e78f4b03d448a8b00ea1ac","tid":1740484,"uid":39470,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-20T02:56:36.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n佢地一直都有出聲"},{"pid":"6bb5647c79722dfeb8dfb19d742cce4a13c2a84a","tid":1740484,"uid":1477,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-20T02:58:49.000Z","msg":"如果你覺得勇武暫時要休息，咁作為和理非嘅你請今晚出場，今晚有行動<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1740320\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1740320</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"363fd9453ad1bc01d3b0ada841fde0381db3cc21","tid":1740484,"uid":12185,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"0b1e87e1b9259093a4e78f4b03d448a8b00ea1ac","tid":1740484,"uid":39470,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-20T02:56:36.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n佢地一直都有出聲"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-20T03:00:11.000Z","msg":"我有留意開<br />\n我係覺得一直都冇點出過聲<br />\n就算有都係主要搞同運<br />\n但6月以黎好似著撚左火咁<br />\n吓吓都直踩政權底線"},{"pid":"37710f0f3db4b0f5e4215f2108472a64438a6ba1","tid":1740484,"uid":249263,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-20T03:00:33.000Z","msg":"法案在參議院通過咗，大家快啲去多謝議員啦！！！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1740143\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1740143</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n幫推<br />\n<br />\nTwitter組24小時keep住更新<br />\n幫手retweet<b