戶係要食好貴手續費<br />\n(chargeback 只限 credit card）"},{"pid":"03964992faa126f8ac3cc6ab6fa2a630482fd1e7","tid":1740484,"uid":12185,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-20T07:26:01.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"9feda9ff950834d91e84249376357f4257d0e82d","tid":1740484,"uid":12185,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-20T07:27:20.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.amnesty.org.hk/en/support-us/donate/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.amnesty.org.hk%2Fen%2Fsupport-us%2Fdonate%2F&d=qnfk3FWFLoR313jZLhvcNtHbQOt8JOG57pMmRaSdLYE%3D&h=12fe2dda\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.amnesty.org.hk/en/support-us/donate/</a><br />\n入錢！入錢！"},{"pid":"46a9e309215abb8c481b74bd7944735ea4935a8a","tid":1740484,"uid":307619,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-20T17:23:24.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7b5c4717aecb8c2994740af10c44df5fa9e02b57","tid":1740484,"uid":12185,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-21T06:23:10.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"eaf4772583c124d0bfa7cc14dee0040ae2bfecdc","tid":1740484,"uid":14494,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-21T06:24:06.000Z","msg":"國際特赦=人權觀察？"},{"pid":"1a281d2b16d4f156b1495ac53f152671204a5a94","tid":1740484,"uid":55162,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-21T06:25:29.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"14620984c8d3c4aa9157093c6d3c027288c65446","tid":1740484,"uid":61511,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"eaf4772583c124d0bfa7cc14dee0040ae2bfecdc","tid":1740484,"uid":14494,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-21T06:24:06.000Z","msg":"國際特赦=人權觀察？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-21T06:29:16.000Z","msg":"好似係兩個黎,但兩個都可以幫<br />\n<br />\n另:國際特赦o係6月已經為香港發聲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=